<TEXT>
<P>
QINGDAO, August 21 (Xinhua) -- The Qingdao Beer Group Co. Ltd.,
China's most famous beer brewery, today signed an agreement with
the Qingdao Branch of Bank of China for a one billion yuan (120
million US dollars) loan.
</P>
