broadened to include cooperation in education," he said.
</P>
<P>
He said Malaysia continues to be impressed by the tremendous
economic achievements of China, consistent with its economic
reforms and opening-up policies.
</P>
<P>
Mahathir said, "In fulfilling the national aspirations of the
people of China for development, the government of China is also
making a singular contribution towards peace, stability and
prosperity in the rest of the region."  
