understanding between the two sides, and advance the two
countries' cooperation in environmental protection to a new level.
</P>
<P>
Xie said China and Romania face similar pollution problems as
their economies grow, and so have a good foundation and future for
cooperation.
</P>
<P>
Oltean expressed great interest in China's environmental
protection work and spoke highly of China's efforts to fight
pollution.
</P>
<P>
Romania is willing to cooperate with China, he said, adding
that his visit is aimed to give a push to the two countries' joint
involvement in environmental protection work.
</P>
<P>
During the meeting, the two sides reached consensus on many
global environmental issues.
</P>
