<HEADLINE> Hong Kong to Join BIS's Bridging Facility to Thailand </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, August 21 (Xinhua) -- The Hong Kong Monetary
Authority (HKMA) said today that it will join the Bank for
International Settlements (BIS) in guaranteeing a short-term
bridging facility to Thailand.
</P>
<P>
