<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Penev Goal Lifts Bulgaria ahead of Russia </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SOFIA, August 20 (Xinhua) -- Veteran Bulgarian striker
Lyuboslav Penev lifted his country to the top of World Cup
European qualifying group five on Wednesday with a 1-0 win over
Israel.
</P>
<P>
Penev's 68th minute strike left the 1994 World Cup
semifinalists one point clear of Russia, with the deciding home
and away clashes between the two yet to come. 
</P>
